<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>dook.zone</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/styles.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/favicon.png" />

        <meta name="theme-color" content="#a4c059" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="nav-bar">
            <ul class="nav-bar-list">
                {% for social in socials %}
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="{{ social.url | url }}"><i class="{{ social.symbol }}"></i>{{ social.name }}</a></li>
                {% endfor %}
                
                <li class="nav-item webring">
                    <a href="https://noodle-r.ing/milomarten/prev" aria-label="Go to previous page in the Amphimorpho web ring"><i class="bi bi-chevron-double-left"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://noodle-r.ing">Amphimorpho Webring</a>
                    <a href="https://noodle-r.ing/milomarten/next" aria-label="Go to next page in the Amphimorpho web ring"><i class="bi bi-chevron-double-right"></i></a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div id="points">
            <section id="fast-facts">
                <h2>Fast Facts</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li class="fact">Name: Milo Marten (AKA Lucbui, Redriders180)</li>
                    <li class="fact">Age: Old (born in 1993)</li>
                    <li class="fact">Pronouns: He/Him</li>
                    <li class="fact">Flags: Aegosexual, Pansexual</li>
                    <li class="fact">Fursonas:
                        <ul>
                            {% for sona in fursonas %}
                            <li class="species">
                                {{ sona.name }} the 
                                {% if sona.species_url %}
                                <a href="{{ sona.species_url | url }}">{{ sona.species }}</a>
                                {% else %}
                                {{ sona.species }}
                                {% endif %}
                                <a class="refsheet" href="refs/{{ sona.name | slugify }}">Reference</a>
                                <a class="refsheet" href="https://bsky.app/hashtag/{{ sona.name | slugify }}?author=milo.dook.zone">Tagged Art</a>
                            </li>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="fact"><abbr title="Original Character">OC</abbr>s:
                        <ul>
                            {% for sona in ocs %}
                            <li class="species">
                                {% if sona.species_url %}
                                {{ sona.name }} the <a href="{{ sona.species_url | url }}">{{ sona.species }}</a> <a class="refsheet" href="refs/{{ sona.name | slugify }}">Reference</a>
                                {% else %}
                                {{ sona.name }} the {{ sona.species }} <a class="refsheet" href="refs/{{ sona.name | slugify }}">Reference</a>
                                {% endif %}
                            </li>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <section id="intro">
                <h2>Howdy!</h2>
                <p>
                    The folks call me Milo Marten. I am a software developer based out of the Dallas/Fort Worth area in Texas, USA. I have been
                    in software dev for about 7 years. I also like LEGO, reading, writing, and drawing. Trains are a particular fascination to me as well, and you'll often find
                    me bouncing across the countryside in pursuit of a locomotive. You can join my Telegram group, where I post all the videos I take, <a href="https://t.me/Chasing_Trains">here</a>!
                </p>
                <p> 
                    I have been formally a furry since 2018, adopting Lucbui the Swolvy. Since then, I have subsequently adopted my namesake Milo, as well as 
                    many other characters (check Fast Facts for them all!). I swap between all of these characters at random, because it's fun :)
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you'd like to hang out with me, hit me up at any of my socials in the navbar! You can also find me at Discord, as "milomarten".
                    I have a Discord server as well, where my best buds can hang out with me!
                </p>
            </section>
            <section id="faq">
                <h2>FAQ</h2>
                <h3>Why does redriders180 sound familiar?</h3>
                <p>
                    You may have played my Pok&#233;mon fan game, Pok&#233;mon Glazed! Initially released in 2012, and completed in 2015, this marked my foray into programming and changed
                    my life forever. I have not worked on it in some years, but I enjoy talking about it...although I don't always remember the things I did or how I did them!
                </p>
                <h3>What's your deal with eggs?</h3>
                <p  aria-label="Pictures of three fried eggs"><i class="bi-egg-fill"></i><i class="bi-egg-fill"></i><i class="bi-egg-fried"></i></p>
            </section>
        </div>
        <footer class="footer">
            <p style="float: left;">Made with <i class="bi-heart-fill" style="color:green;"></i> by Milo Marten</p>
            <p style="float: right;">Background art made by <a href="https://twitter.com/orcaowlart">OrcaOwl</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/SpikieAMR">SpikieAMR</a>!</p>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>